outputs.output_descr:
Namibia's First Biennial Update Report  (BUR 1) for the Greenhouse Gas Inventory to the UNFCCC.
Namibia's First Biennial Update (BUR1 NAM) to the UNFCCC Project involves the preparation of BUR1 for submission to the Conference of Parties (COP) of the UNFCCC in accordance with its commitment as a party to the Convention as per Decision 2/CP.17 taken at COP 17. The BUR will be the first for Namibia and it will be conducted in complimentary with Namibia's Third National Communication (NC3)building on and updating work carried out under the previous National Communications
